data.description:
Welcome home to this beautiful landscaped brick cape cod in St. Matthews. This home features hardwood floors, partially finished basement and breezeway to 1 car garage. The second floor master suite has an abundance of closet space and features a bonus room currently being used as a nursery. Built in shelving in the basement is great for storage. Enjoy cookouts on the deck and brick patio in the fenced in backyard. 

Seller also the listing agent.
